S.FORM: I 1945 a miheca saka 1 folad saka 29 a romi'ad masofoc ci Ibrahim Boubacar Keïta , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Mali anini i ci Ibrahim Boubacar Keïta, patirengan a romi'ad i 2013 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 4 a romi'ad.
